Package: medshift
Title: Causal mediation analysis for stochastic interventions
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Nima", "Hejazi", email = "nhejazi@berkeley.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7127-2789")),
    person("Iván", "Díaz", email = "ild2005@med.cornell.edu",
           role = c("aut"))
  )
Maintainer: Nima Hejazi <nh@nimahejazi.org>
Description: Tools for efficiently estimating parameters of a decomposition of
    the population intervention effect when performing causal mediation
    analysis. An implementation accompanying the manuscript "Causal mediation
    analysis for stochastic interventions" (Díaz & Hejazi, 2018+).
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
